                <h1>The Unnamed Narrator of The Yellow Wallpaper</h1>
                <p>The narrator of "The Yellow Wallpaper" is an unnamed woman who struggles with mental illness and confinement in her surroundings. Her internal journey is depicted through her obsession with the wallpaper in her room, which becomes a symbol of her entrapment and fight for self-identity as she descends into madness.</p>
